      "span_text": "Oligonucleotides complementary to the 5′ and 3′ ends of the human Fe65 coding sequence were synthesized (5′ probe, 5′-GGC CTC CTC CGC CAA GGT CAA GGT CAC ATT GCG ATT CTG GTC-3′; 3′ probe, 5′-CAA GTT TAG AGT GGT CCA GGG AGA GTC CAT TTA CCA AGC AGC G-3′; Integrated DNA Technologies, IA) and labeled with [CITATION_2] S-ATP using terminal deoxynucleotidyl transferase (Promega, WI).",
